###  http://www.semanticweb.org/kaik/ontologies/2026/3/ivd-mrh-ontology#actionDate
<http://www.semanticweb.org/kaik/ontologies/2026/3/ivd-mrh-ontology#actionDate> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
