:NearMissIncident rdf:type owl:Class ;
                  rdfs:subClassOf :Incident ;
                  owl:disjointWith :SeriousIncident ;
                  rdfs:comment "An incident that did not result in harm, damage, or loss, but had a potential to do so."@en ;
                  rdfs:label "NearMissIncident"@en .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/kaik/ontologies/2026/3/ivd-high-risk-medical-devices-eu#PatientHarm
